706239f-a.title: Brooklyn: Pennsylvania Avenue - Liberty Avenue
706239f-a.text:
Pennsylvania Ave., at the S.W. corner of Liberty Ave., showing the
Y.M.C.A building in 1912. Ihn 1929, this building housed the Polish Demo-
cratic Club of the 22nd Assembly District of Brooklyn.
April 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
